<div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div first  avia-builder-el-21  el_before_av_one_fourth  avia-builder-el-first  " ><article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-22  avia-builder-el-no-sibling "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class="iconbox_content"><header class="entry-content-header"><a href='http://www2.cnv.org:8085/webcat/request/DoMenuRequest?SystemName=North+Vancouver+Archives&UserName=web+test&Password=web&TemplateProcessID=1004_452_1151&bCachable=1&MenuName=Search%20Holdings%20%28public%20interface%29' title='Archives Database'  class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'  ></a><h3 class='iconbox_content_title'  itemprop="headline"  ><a href='http://www2.cnv.org:8085/webcat/request/DoMenuRequest?SystemName=North+Vancouver+Archives&UserName=web+test&Password=web&TemplateProcessID=1004_452_1151&bCachable=1&MenuName=Search%20Holdings%20%28public%20interface%29' title='Archives Database' >Archives Database</a></h3></header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop="text"  ><p class="p1">Search NVMA’s Archives Database from home OR to learn about our major archives collections and programs, visit the <a title="Archives Collections" href="http://nvma.ca/collections/archive-collections/">Archives Collection </a>page.</p>
</div></div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article></div><div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-23  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_one_fourth  " style='border-radius:0px; '><article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-24  avia-builder-el-no-sibling "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class="iconbox_content"><header class="entry-content-header"><a href='http://nvma.ca/collections/museum-collection/' title='Museum Collection'  class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'  ></a><h3 class='iconbox_content_title'  itemprop="headline"  ><a href='http://nvma.ca/collections/museum-collection/' title='Museum Collection' >Museum Collection</a></h3></header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop="text"  ><p>Explore North Vancouver’s fascinating history through its collection of significant and unique objects.</p>
</div></div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article></div><div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-25  el_after_av_one_fourth  el_before_av_one_fourth  " style='border-radius:0px; '><article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-26  avia-builder-el-no-sibling "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class="iconbox_content"><header class="entry-content-header"><a href='http://nvma.ca/exhibits-events/virtual-exhibits/' title='Virtual Exhibits'  class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'  ></a><h3 class='iconbox_content_title'  itemprop="headline"  ><a href='http://nvma.ca/exhibits-events/virtual-exhibits/' title='Virtual Exhibits' >Virtual Exhibits</a></h3></header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop="text"  ><p>Browse highlights from our local histories. See original documents, artifacts, historic photographs and hear stories from our mountaineers.</p>
</div></div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article></div><div class="flex_column av_one_fourth  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-27  el_after_av_one_fourth  avia-builder-el-last  " style='border-radius:0px; '><article class="iconbox iconbox_left   avia-builder-el-28  avia-builder-el-no-sibling "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class="iconbox_content"><header class="entry-content-header"><div class="iconbox_icon heading-color" aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'  ></div><h3 class='iconbox_content_title'  itemprop="headline"  ><a href='http://nvma.ca/history' title='North Van History'  >North Van History</a></h3></header><div class='iconbox_content_container '  itemprop="text"  ><p>From the shoreline to the mountains, this community has remarkable stories to share. <a title="History" href="http://nvma.ca/history/">More</a></p>
</div></div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article></div>

